_sText:
A new Christmas map by me for the third year running, with a bonus made by bhopshawty.

Wish I had more time, lots of things that were placeholders never got changed.

Hope you enjoy nonetheless.

P.S. The ice seems to not work as well on higher ping, sorry.

Edit: Reupload bsp cause bonus end mod zone was accidentally labelled as start so fixed that. Since it's less than a day later I didn't rename the bsp. It's always something eh? Also made bonus song loop quicker as was intended.
